Interface IEntity

All Known Implementing Classes:
Applicant, Enquiry, Manager, Officer, Project, ProjectApplication, ProjectRegistration, Reply, User
public interface IEntity
Generic interface representing an entity that can be stored and retrieved from a CSV file. Entities implementing this interface must be identifiable by a unique ID and support serialization/deserialization to and from CSV format.
